Igba ọsọ na ihu igwe bụ ihe ngosi nkè Robert Alstead na Joanna Clarke nke icecle.ca productions Ltd
Ihe nkiri ahụ na-elekwasị anya na mkpọsa ntuli aka n'afọ 2013 nke ónyé ọkà mmụta sayensị ihu igwe Andrew J
Weaver dị ka ónyé mbụ Green Party Member nke Nzukọ omeiwu na British Columbia, Canada.
Igba ọsọ na ihu igwe malitere na DOXA Documentary Film Festival na Vancouver n'ọnwa Mee afọ 2015.
